{
  "stem": "1641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "If they saw something, somebody not stepping on time, then they came over and gave us a big bash on the face.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "That was lucky, because the old-timers said previous years they used to shoot them right away on the spot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But in my time, by-- by middle of '44, they only bashed them up or kicked them or punched them in the eye or somewhere.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We went to the workplace, and there we had to-- there was a Polish kapo who was beating everybody, because we're not used to-- we-- we had to be broken in to [? hard. ?] We had to take the bags of potatoes-- so the men not walking, but running with it.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had to run with it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we only had wooden clogs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was very hard to run in a wooden clog.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, Dutch-- only a piece of timber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And to run in it with a heavy bag on your back, it's very, very difficult.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And if it was not quick, if you dropped it, then-- then he came there and hit you 10 times for it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So that was the work in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Well, I could go on for hours.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's-- at lunchtime, we had half an hour break.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Then we had a soup, which was mostly potato peel and a bit of cabbage in it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And then in the evening, marched-- we marched back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And doesn't matter, rain or whatever.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was luckily summer, so it was only cold in the morning.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "A lot of rain.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "If you were wet, then you had to sleep in the wet uniform-- no-- no nightgown or pajamas, of course.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We got back.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "The worst thing was I remember a couple very bad days.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
